之蝶要來森林玩的時間了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev203-ep4-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"牠只會出現５分鐘我得趕快去才行！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"ev203-ep4-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"七深，在嗎～？　我有一件想做的衣服啊～。\n幫我收集素材……咦，人跑去哪裡了啊？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"ev203-ep4-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"真白","body":"啊，小透，你看，這個牌子。\n上面寫著『廣町外出中，有空的話就看看我珍藏的\n收藏品等等我喔～』","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"ev203-ep4-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"咦～，那就稍微等一下吧。\n怎麼好像比之前來的時候，多了更多收藏啊？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionCh